name: Tess Taylor Arlington
description:
For @jjonahjameson

Tess Taylor Arlington is an American Actress, Reality TV star and Cyber Girl of the Week July 2009 and Cyber Girl of the Year 2010.

Trained on 1.5 base model but examples are from Analog Madness and Consistent Factor.

As you might suspected, since she is a Playboy model this will skew towards NSFW, but there is another clothed pictures in the training that it is not difficult ro produce SFW images too

Any Feedback or suggestions for a POTM to do next is greatly welcomed
